OL,6,FShalma Pervin has witnessed some of
OL,7,Fthe horrors taking place there herself
OL,8,Fafter visiting the country.
OL,10,FShe said: "I saw one guy, he got shot
OL,11,Fon the head. He was bleeding on the
OL,12,Feyes, everywhere.
OL,14,F"I saw the blood on the road and one
OL,15,Fday I got tear gassed and I felt like
OL,16,FI was nearly blind."
