OL,3,CFamilies 'very anxious' for relatives
OL,4,Cin Bangladesh as unrest continues
OL,6,FFazlul Haque Farooque has not lived in
OL,7,FBangladesh for 50 years but the pain
OL,8,Fof seeing what is happening is deeply
OL,9,Fupsetting - he hoped things would
OL,10,Fimprove as time went on.
OL,12,F"It makes me now more worried," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We thought it would settle a bit as
OL,16,Fit gets longer, we though, it'd get
OL,17,Fbetter.
