OL,6,F"But after this event we are now
OL,7,Fthinking twice at what will be the
OL,8,Ffuture and what will be with our
OL,9,Ffamily and everyone who is left there."
OL,11,FRumana Faruque said her aunt cut a
OL,12,Ftrip to Wales short so she could fly
OL,13,Fback to Bangladesh to be with her son
OL,14,Fand make sure he was safe.
OL,16,FMs Faruque said: "You can't really
OL,17,Fenjoy a holiday or anything if you
OL,18,Fthink that your son is going to be
OL,19,Fbombarded or he could be dead at any
OL,20,Fmoment on the street.
