OL,6,F"We are very anxious but looking at my
OL,7,Faunt's face, this was the right
OL,8,Fdecision..she just wanted to fly and
OL,9,Fget back to her children."
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sheikh Hasina - who
OL,12,Fruled Bangladesh for 15 years - quit
OL,13,Fher role last Monday (5 July),
OL,14,Ffollowing weeks of anti-government
OL,15,Fprotests that culminated with
OL,16,Fdemonstrators entering her official
OL,17,Fresidence.
