OL,6,FThe head of Bangladesh's military has
OL,7,Fsaid he will assume temporary control
OL,8,Fof the country until an interim
OL,9,Fgovernment is formed but the country
OL,10,Fis still left in a climate of
OL,11,Fpolitical uncertainty.
OL,13,FBangladesh's main opposition party has
OL,14,Furged people to exercise restraint in
OL,15,Fwhat it said was a "transitional
OL,16,Fmoment on our democratic path".
