OL,6,FVolker Turk, the United Nation's (UN)
OL,7,Fhuman rights chief, also said the
OL,8,Ftransition of power in Bangladesh must
OL,9,Fbe "in line with the country's
OL,10,Finternational obligations" and
OL,11,F"inclusive and open to the meaningful
OL,12,Fparticipation of all Bangladeshis".
